## Third-Party Components

This project incorporates or depends on various open-source components:

- **Kubernetes** (Apache 2.0) - Container orchestration
- **Helm** (Apache 2.0) - Kubernetes package manager
- **Ansible** (GPL v3.0) - Configuration management
- **Keycloak** (Apache 2.0) - Identity and access management
- **PostgreSQL** (PostgreSQL License) - Database system
- **Redis** (BSD 3-Clause) - In-memory data store
- **Grafana** (Apache 2.0) - Monitoring and observability
- **Prometheus** (Apache 2.0) - Monitoring system

For detailed license information of all components, please refer to their respective repositories and documentation.

